data.description: This incredible home has four bedrooms, three bathrooms, formal living room, and central air conditioning! The kitchen, dining and family room are open concept and conducive to entertaining and hosting guests. A large master bedroom upstairs features a 5 piece ensuite with a huge walk in closet. On the upper level, you'll find all four bedrooms and a loft area that provides an amazing flex space.  The basement is pre-plumbed for a bathroom and has plenty of unfinished space for you to imagine and create whatever you'd like to add... perhaps a theater room, a home gym, or a playroom? A terraced back yard provides a spacious concrete patio for dining or lounging. Only minutes to most military installations! This home is a must see!
